  <!-- DELIVERY HOSPITAL -->
  <category>
    <pattern>DELIVERY HOSPITAL</pattern>
    <template>For delivery, go to the nearest government PHC, CHC, or District Hospital.
Under JSSK scheme, delivery is COMPLETELY FREE including:
- Normal and C-section delivery
- Medicines and food during stay
- Free transport from home and back
Type HOSPITAL IN followed by your district to find the nearest facility.
For emergency delivery, call 108 immediately — ambulance is FREE.</template>
  </category>

  <!-- MENTAL HEALTH -->
  <category>
    <pattern>MENTAL HEALTH</pattern>
    <template>Mental Health Support:
📞 iCall Helpline: 9152987821 (Free counselling — Mon to Sat, 8am-10pm)
🏥 Free treatment available at District Hospital psychiatry OPD under NMHP
If someone is in crisis or danger — call 112 immediately.
It is okay to ask for help. Mental health is as important as physical health.</template>
  </category>

